data.description: Big investment opportunity!  Come own a piece of history!  Great opportunity to house hack and live in one unit and rent the other two units. Commercial building with two apartment units attached upstairs.  The commercial building hosts the new and best upcoming restaurant in Bethel.  It offers 2000 sq ft with a full kitchen and two bathrooms.  The upstairs units have 2 bedrooms and 1 bath each.  Commercial unit rents out for $1,000 a month with room to increase rent. Restaurant is on a 2 year lease.  The upstairs units rent out for $1050 and $900.  Restaurant operator owns all the equipment.  Each unit pays their own utilities besides garbage and water. Huge opportunity awaits with insane ROI and Cap Rates.  Over 16,000 cars pass this building daily. Please do not disturb restaurant owner or tenant.  One unit is vacant for showings. Unit 2 will be viewed during the inspection period  Restaurant is open from 8am-2pm everyday.  Do not walk back in the kitchen area when the restaurant is operating. Need 24 hour notice to view.  Building is agent owned.
